title: CADET KELLY R5
description:
In CADET KELLY, a free-spirited 14-year-old must go back to basics in discipline, training, and attire -- when she&#039;s forced to join a military academy. Hilary Duff ("Lizzie McGuire") stars as carefree Kelly Collins, a teenager jolted out of the creative freedom and artistic expression enjoyed at her New York City school when her divorced mom marries a lifelong military man (Gary Cole) who&#039;s the new commandant at George Washington Academy in upstate New York -- and Kelly is his newest recruit. Nearly crushed into conformity, the indefatigable Kelly makes the best of the situation despite the fact that her Cadet Captain, the cold-hearted Jennifer Stone (Christy Carlson Romano "Even Stevens"), is bent on providing the worst experience possible. Soon Kelly actually starts to see benefits in military school, especially after she makes the drill team and impresses upperclassmen Brad (Shawn Ashmore). But can a formerly flaky artist ever really become a true blue cadet? Kelly must answer that herself when the drill team&#039;s championship depends on her, but the pressure to win from her stepfather could make her go AWOL. 



Language(s): English


Approximate Run Time: 100 minutes
